track_notes: Had a great hike From Parking to the summit. The views over the ocean are spectacular.

4 trails approach Sargent Mountain summit. This route starts Northwest of the summit, at the trail head, on route 3, about 3 miles north of Northeast Harbor, and follows the Giant slide trail for the first mile. Then left onto the Sargent Mountain North Ridge trail. Nice hike.
track_title: Route to Sargent Mountain from the Northwest, via Giant Slide.
